arts.ttl: Gone in 42 minutes: Cristiano Ronaldo hits incredible 24-year milestone
arts.sum: The Portuguese star scored his 917th career goal from the penalty spot, turning the game around and securing a victory against Al Okhdood, who had taken an early lead. True to form, 2025 was no exception, as it took just 42 minutes into his first match of the year for Ronaldo to celebrate his first goal, orchestrating yet another victory for Al Nassr.

arts.ttl: Cristiano Ronaldo and Al Nassr rev up for 2025
arts.sum: The Portuguese star will be hoping that the opening game of the new year, against lowly Al Okhdood offers an opportunity to find the net in this milestone year for the player. The new year commences for Cristiano Ronaldo this Thursday when Al Nassr host Al Okhdood as part of Matchday 14 in the Roshn Saudi League .

arts.ttl: Preview: Al-Nassr vs. Al Okhdood - prediction, team news, lineups
arts.sum: Sports Mole previews Thursday's Saudi Pro League clash between Al-Nassr and Al Okhdood, including predictions, team news and possible lineups.
